Show HN: ParallelGPT â€“ Batch processing with ChatGPT on low-code spreadsheet UI
text:
We made ParallelGPT - a tool that lets you bulk process chatGPT on a spreadsheet UI instead of one-by-one conversation style. Hopefully this saves you time and hassle - especially if you want to build an operational process around it and want to collaborate your team.

You can give it a quick spin on this live demo playground: https://demo.rowy.io/table/parallelGpt#sideDrawer=%22table-i...

I am the co-founder of Rowy(https://www.rowy.io), an open-source low-code platform, and we built ParallelGPT as a fun showcase of what you can do with low-code.

There are tons of exciting AI apps you can build with low-code, and we're always happy to chat about any ideas you have and assist on our Discord.
